gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 128, Bucks 119
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Tyrese Haliburtons 27 points, seven rebounds and 15 assists, the Pacers defeated the Bucks, 128-119 and advance to the IST Championship. Myles Turner added 26 points and 10 rebounds, while Giannis Antetokounmpo (37 points, 10 rebounds, two blocks) and Damian Lillard (24 points, seven rebounds, seven assists) combined for 61 points for the Bucks in the losing effort.  The Pacers improve to 12-8 on the season, while the Bucks fall to 15-7.
